Monitor S3 Buckets- The most common tool to analyze S3 Buckets is CloudTrail together with Amazon Cloudwatch.
Cloudtrail provides a record of actions taken by a user,role or an AWS Service, for example you can determine the IP origin from which the request was made.

With Cloudwatch is possible to create Alarms. If the metric exceeds of this specific threshold, a notification is sent to an Amazon SNS topic.

On the SQS scenario using too Cloudwatch integrated on the Queue is possible to view and analyze metrics for Amazon SQS queues.


